{"tid":1775053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩臥底遊戲嗰三個FA入嚟","createTime":"2019-12-08T15:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T17:51:20.000Z","uid":231425,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da16acada0f3fa12f44e1e4fc125df01e3410697","tid":1775053,"uid":231425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDVaJ6H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDVaJ6H.jpg&h=b4e1a46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我屌撚晒你哋老母</span><br />\n唔知你啲相幾時影<br />\n你哋玩得咁嘅野 俾人影到相<br />\n就要負責任 出嚟道歉<br />\n托人出個澄清把鬼啊？<br />\n<br />\n而家咁多人出嚟做FA<br />\n係因為我哋已經冇乜人信得過<br />\n醫院急症室有曱甴 醫管局俾曱甴接管<br />\n救護車俾曱甴攔<br />\n睇私家都有仆街篤灰<br />\n手足就嚟去到未死得都唔敢睇醫生嘅地歩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手足已經只係信FA可以幫到佢哋</span><br />\n<br />\n你哋而家玩啲咁嘅野 仲俾人瘋傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">破壞晒市民同手足對同路人FA嘅信任</span></span><br />\n你估個個都會睇留言有冇FC有冇炒車先share？老老實實黃絲一樣大把人傳誤信謠言仲要四圍傳<br />\n<br />\n更重要嘅係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋對唔撚對得住811銅鑼灣俾班blackbloc曱甴背叛嘅手足？<br />\n仲有佢哋嘅手足 屋企人 朋友？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tGCwtyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtGCwtyx.jpg&h=2a70e74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我再一次屌撚晒你哋老母<br />\n出嚟道歉啊<br />\n<br />\nFA啟"},{"pid":"eba899f9d26bd36ef06e126259c2587a6252a2cc","tid":1775053,"uid":328673,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da16acada0f3fa12f44e1e4fc125df01e3410697","tid":1775053,"uid":231425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDVaJ6H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDVaJ6H.jpg&h=b4e1a46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我屌撚晒你哋老母</span><br />\n唔知你啲相幾時影<br />\n你哋玩得咁嘅野 俾人影到相<br />\n就要負責任 出嚟道歉<br />\n托人出個澄清把鬼